column5: Trying to find out who caught the biggest walleye on Lac Seul last year. How big....What Bait...Thanks

My Buddy caught a 30" 11lb 5oz wall hanger last August. Caught her on a jig and Leech. Hooked her in front of what we call Shore Lunch Island 1/2 mile southeast of Fish Gut Bay. Released her and had a replica made.
